### Render ListEventTypes Atom

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/atoms/list-event-types.mdx

This snippet shows how to render the ListEventTypes atom, which displays a user's event types. It requires wrapping in CalProvider with authentication credentials. The getEventTypeUrl prop is optional and defines the redirect URL for each event type.

```tsx
import { CalProvider, ListEventTypes } from "@calcom/atoms";

export default function EventTypesPage() {
  return (
    <CalProvider clientId="your-client-id" accessToken="user-access-token">
      <ListEventTypes getEventTypeUrl={(eventTypeId) => `/event-types/${eventTypeId}`} />
    </CalProvider>
  );
}
```

